For testing/troubleshooting convinience.

make vm-boot-serial-<guest>
  Boot guest, with the serial console on stdio.

make vm-boot-ssh-<guest>
  Boot guest, login via ssh.

Signed-off-by: Gerd Hoffmann <kraxel@redhat.com>
---
